@node  Requirements

                          @{b}SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS@{ub}
                                               
     *  Amiga Running Workbench 3.0 or Better.
             
     *  The Faster the processor the Better.
                                   
     *  Should run on a standard Amiga A1200 not Tested can't be bothered
        to pull board out.
               
     *  Will work with 2Megs but don't expect much with 2Megs of anything.
           
     *  The more Memory the better.
                 
     *  Written on an Amiga A1200 040 16MB OS 3.5.                               
            
                                                                                                      
            @{b}-----------------------------------------------@{ub}    
                              
                      @{"BACK TO INDEX" link Main}

@endnode
